  "commentary": "**DEALER HEDGING COMMENTARY:**\n\nWith SPX at 6553 trading below the 6576 flip strike in PIN regime, dealers are long gamma and actively buying this dip while providing stabilizing flow against the recent volatility surge. The massive +13.7B gamma wall at 6580 creates a strong magnet effect above current levels, while the thick positive gamma cushion from 6565-6580 should cap upside momentum and encourage mean reversion toward 6565-6570. Watch for dealer selling pressure to intensify if we push through 6576 toward the 6580 max gamma strike, but expect continued dip-buying support above the 6500 negative gamma floor where dealer buying would amplify any breakdown.",
